l do your bit of washing or - and they used to help one an other in that way. Sort of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14707464\charrsid6628200 backwards}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5733652\charrsid6628200  and forwards sort of thing.

